  "description": "<h3><strong>Security Engineer</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Salary Range: $2.4k - $2.8k</strong></li><li><strong>Gross Salary Range: $2.8k - $3.2k </strong></li><li><strong>Working Days: 4 days (16 shifts per month) </strong></li><li><strong>Working Hours: 12-hr rotating shift, 7.30am-7.30pm, 7.30pm-7.30am</strong></li><li><strong>Location: Jurong East/Toh Guan</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Responding to intrusion alarm system activation</li><li>Performing maintenance service, commissioning of alarm systems.</li><li>Attending to customer request on alarm and card access systems</li><li>Conducting patrols at night</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Possess at least a Higher Nitec</li><li>Valid class 3 license</li><li>1-2 years relevant working experience</li><li>With Enhanced Basic Security certification will be an added advantage.</li></ul><p><br />Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
